### Register (password min 8 characters)
### Use a valid email: domain after @ must be real, e.g. gmail.com — not "amanyadav@.com"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "amanyadav@gmail.com",
  "password": "password12"
}

### Login (same email + password as register)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "amanyadav@gmail.com",
  "password": "password12"
}

### Health (no auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health

### Swagger UI (browser): http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html
### OpenAPI JSON (Postman import): http://localhost:8080/v3/api-docs

### --- Tasks (JWT) ---
### Set @token to accessToken only (no extra word "token" at the end — copy ends with ...chars like AI8 not AI8token)
### Use: Authorization: Bearer {{token}}   OR raw JWT: Authorization: {{token}}
### WRONG: {{eyJ...}} around the whole JWT — {{ }} is only for variable NAMES like {{token}}

@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhbWFueWFkYXZAZ21haWwuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3Mjg2MzEsImV4cCI6MTc3NDgxNTAzMX0.1oYWiR_P4X0tVIVOlCW179RIHojdWsLuaSF1u3wHZOI

### List tasks (USER: own tasks only; ADMIN: all tasks)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhbWFueWFkYXZAZ21haWwuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3Mjg2MzEsImV4cCI6MTc3NDgxNTAzMX0.1oYWiR_P4X0tVIVOlCW179RIHojdWsLuaSF1u3wHZOI

### Create task (optional status: TODO | IN_PROGRESS | DONE; omit for TODO)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhbWFueWFkYXZAZ21haWwuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3Mjg2MzEsImV4cCI6MTc3NDgxNTAzMX0.1oYWiR_P4X0tVIVOlCW179RIHojdWsLuaSF1u3wHZOI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first task",
  "description": "Optional description",
  "status": "TODO"
}

### Get task by id (use id from create/list response, e.g. 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhbWFueWFkYXZAZ21haWwuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3Mjg2MzEsImV4cCI6MTc3NDgxNTAzMX0.1oYWiR_P4X0tVIVOlCW179RIHojdWsLuaSF1u3wHZOI

### Update task (same id; status must be TODO | IN_PROGRESS | DONE)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhbWFueWFkYXZAZ21haWwuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3Mjg2MzEsImV4cCI6MTc3NDgxNTAzMX0.1oYWiR_P4X0tVIVOlCW179RIHojdWsLuaSF1u3wHZOI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Authorization : Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhbWFueWFkYXZAZ21haWwuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3Mjg2MzEsImV4cCI6MTc3NDgxNTAzMX0.1oYWiR_P4X0tVIVOlCW179RIHojdWsLuaSF1u3wHZOI


### Delete task (204 No Content if ok)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhbWFueWFkYXZAZ21haWwuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3Mjg2MzEsImV4cCI6MTc3NDgxNTAzMX0.1oYWiR_P4X0tVIVOlCW179RIHojdWsLuaSF1u3wHZOI
